{"tid":1489624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民上裝，唔係講笑！","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T04:11:43.000Z","uid":167802,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"29cc33157dcf612d767d3a96431fee6870d7c61a","tid":1489624,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"將軍澳斬人案再次證明香港警察嘅無能<br />\n有晒片，CCTV，出入記錄到而家都未拉倒人?<br />\n若非無能，就只有<span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作</span>呢個可能性!<br />\n所以我哋唔可以再靠警察保護自己!<br />\n<br />\n如果你係唔想咁易受傷嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">爬山時一定要有防具喺身</span></span><br />\n頭盔，頸箍，甲，千流明電筒，乜都好<br />\n唔好淨係得個大膽!<br />\n而今次事件仲有個好重要嘅教訓，就係<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防備陌生人</span></span>!<br />\n我明白大家都好有心想去將自己嘅講法同香港人分享，但事態緊急! 唔好一味得個勇! 有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有任何可疑之處嘅男人</span></span>行近嘅時候，計可以照傾，但<span style=\"color: red;\">馬上進入戒備狀態，攞定防具</span>! 如果怕嚇親對方，或者對方顯得有防備，同佢<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解釋</span></span>。如果係正常人，一定會明白你哋嘅防禦態勢! 如果係鬼，大家識做!<br />\n<br />\n我係咪勸緊大家唔好再爬山?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係!</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正正因為必須繼續爬山，所以先要保護好自己。咁唔係懦弱，咁先係真正勇武!</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6ecfc988032228c8bcadeccee66317a344c8346","tid":1489624,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"14c1ec526cef99f97c16f1ab9fb59b235422f78c","tid":1489624,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:16:27.000Z